# GymRoutine Mobile Project Structure

This is a SwiftUI-based iOS application with a Firebase backend for gym workout tracking and social features.

## Main Directories

- **gymroutine-mobile/**: Main iOS app codebase
  - [Application/gymroutine_mobileApp.swift](mdc:gymroutine-mobile/Application/gymroutine_mobileApp.swift): App entry point and configuration
  - [Application/Router.swift](mdc:gymroutine-mobile/Application/Router.swift): Navigation router
  
- **Features/**: Contains the main app features organized by domain
  - Home: Home screen views
  - Exercise: Exercise management
  - Workout: Workout tracking
  - Calendar: Schedule views
  - Profile: User profile management
  - Analytics: Usage analytics
  - Root: Root view components

- **Services/**: Service layer for API calls and external integrations

- **Models/**: Data models and entities

- **Repositories/**: Data access layer

- **Manager/**: Business logic managers

- **ViewParts/**: Reusable UI components

- **Extensions/**: Swift extension utilities

## Backend

- **backend/functions/**: Firebase Cloud Functions
- **backend/firebase.json**: Firebase configuration
